# ⏱️ Complexity Analysis

### Time Complexity

```text
O(n log n)
```

- Sorting the array dominates the runtime.

### Space Complexity

```text
O(1)
```

- Ignoring the space used by sorting.

---

# 🧠 Key Insight

To maximize savings, the free candy should be as expensive as possible.

Sorting in descending order ensures that in every group of three candies, the third candy (which becomes free) has the highest possible value among the remaining candies.

